# PR-188 / session 188 — Vite `publicDir` for the SPA. Anything dropped
# here is served at the SPA root (e.g. `aberp-logo.png` → `/aberp-logo.png`).
# Convention is documented in the README under "Branding the SPA header".
#
# The directory MUST exist at build time (Vite reads it during `vite build`),
# but the actual operator-supplied branding assets are private and MUST NOT
# land in git. Track this `.gitignore` so the directory survives a clone;
# ignore everything else.
*
!.gitignore

# Áben brand DEFAULTS ship with the product (they are the fallback identity
# rendered when no operator logo is present) — distinct from the private
# operator-supplied assets above, so they MUST be tracked or a fresh clone /
# CI `vite build` would 404 the favicon and lose the mark.
!favicon.svg
!brand-mark.svg
